title: Jokes Books Collection - Mantesh
description:
===================================

Jokes Books Collection - Mantesh

1. A Dictionary of Slang and Unconventional English: Colloquialisms and Catch Phrases, Fossilised Jokes and Puns, General Nicknames, Vulgarisms, and Such Americanisms As Have Been Naturalised - Eric Partridge 

2. Don't kid yourself: relatively great (family) jokes - Sam Schultz, Brian Gable 

3. God Loves Golfers Best: The Best Jokes, Quotes, and Cartoons for Golfers - Ray Foley

4. Practical Jokes: Heartless Hoaxes and Cunning Tricks to Humiliate Friend and Foe - Lorenz Books 

5. Plato and a Platypus Walk into a Bar: Understanding Philosophy Through Jokes - Thomas Cathcart, Daniel Klein

6. Surely You're Joking, Mr. Feynman! : Adventures of a Curious Character - Richard P. Feynman

7. The Bumper B3ta Book of Sick Jokes - Rob Manuel 

8. The Everything Kids' Joke Book: Side-Splitting, Rib-Tickling Fun - Michael Dahl 

9. The Friars Club Encyclopedia of Jokes: Revised and Updated! Over 2,000 One-Liners, Straight Lines, Stories, Gags, Roasts, Ribs, and Put-Downs - Friars Club

10. The Little Book of Dirty Jokes (Summersdale humour: the little book of...) - Ed Cobham 

11. Truth Be Told: Off the Record about Favorite Guests, Memorable Moments, Funniest Jokes, and a Half Century of Asking Questions - Larry King
